"She was at the Holesovice Exhibition Park at a party."
“What’s interesting is that it didn’t seem weird to the mother that her daughter was away for 48 hours,” the director of the department said.
It is precisely the disinterestedness of the parents or their unusual tolerance to the fact that their rejections indulge in the drink that are the main cause of the development of alcoholism of children.
According to specialists, however, we are not talking about addiction, in its strict sense, for children.
"Under the term alcoholic we mean a chronic dependence on alcohol for several years with all the phenomena that result from it but that are not found in children."
“In those who use the acool repeatedly, it is rather a significantly unfavorable socio-family background,” explained the Pelikan Head of Department.
