If it does, it needs to gain the support of the middle class, among which Kirchnerism is very much in demand.
When the Argentines will return from their summer vacation in March, the wave of sympathy for her will have receded.
If she wants to win another election, she will have to decide whether or not to repudiate, without noise, many of her husband's policies.
